{"type": "article", "id": 40401, "title": "Coach 净利润大涨，以及，MUJI 推出可乐饮料 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-05-03T02:50:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 264, "name": "MUJI"}, {"id": 799, "name": "大都会艺术博物馆"}, {"id": 906, "name": "川久保玲"}, {"id": 6058, "name": "可乐"}, {"id": 23756, "name": "MET"}, {"id": 40041, "name": "Nike Air VaporMax"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}, {"id": 6654, "name": "Etsy"}, {"id": 18765, "name": "藤原浩"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170503093409l7ZTt8ozjCPGFYns.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://thefemin.com/2017/05/zara-just-launched-a-clever-online-shopping-tool/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>为减少退货率，Zara 美国版网站推出新功能</strong></a> | 消费者只需要点击商品下方的“What's My Size”，然后输入自己的身高和体重，Zara 就会自动找出最合适的尺码。推出这项功能后，Zara 将可减少消费者因码数不合适而退货的情况。同时，Zara 也在提高实体门店的数字化水平，在最新开设的全球最大旗舰店中，已开始实行自助付款和智能试衣等功能。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/coach-posts-q3-profits-bested-wall-streets-estimates-2-cents-handbags-accessories-retail-10878965/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Coach 发布第三季度财报，净利润上升 8.6%</strong></a> | Coach 集团提升全价产品销售的策略开始生效，净利润上升 8.6%，达到 1.2 亿美元，不过策略调整也使得净销售额下降了 3.2%。该财报发布后，Coach 股价开盘大涨 10.48% 至每股 42.77 美元，目前市值约为 118.3 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/etsy-replaces-ceo-chad-dickerson-plans-to-cut-staff-as-revenues-grow-10879524/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国手工艺品电商平台 Etsy 任命新的 CEO，计划裁员 8%</strong></a> |日前，Etsy 决定任命 Josh Silverman 接替 Chad Dickerson 为 CEO。Josh Silverman 此前是 Skype 和 Shopping.com 的CEO，Chad Dickerson 于 2011 年出任 Etsy 的 CEO，将于 5 月底离职。在宣布此决定的同时，Etsy 还表示为控制运营成本，计划裁员 80人，即 8% 的员工。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>藤原浩与 Kim Jones 牵头的<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/fragment-design-x-louis-vuitton-pop-up-london-harrods\" rel=\"nofollow\"> fragment design x Louis Vuitton 企划来到伦敦</a>，在时尚百货 Harrods 开设全新快闪店。除了服装、皮具、鞋履与配件外，店内还有不少 Harrods 快闪店限定商品，这次店铺将持续运营到 5 月 21 日。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103049FsI5HthOlj9S8kuY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103049ObEFt0JW8M4m7yav.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705031030497mRsLMlYBepnZSJr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103050ablCkwWQzy4TDuF3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103052hVyZJWlBENOdsSGn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103052slm4ufLy5aYEjOVH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103052KWdlcoJ0Ej2bQ5yz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103053VUYnF9oRPMQ0dL4y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103053S3hKMo6HiPzwdsAJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103054nTClyc4bQIYSx1F0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103054nC27jKzMLBcbQuAD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017050310305654tmxYfAWc2h9Rny.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103056zG4XJ59shOf207ck.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103056Lu0pTmn59lUF8hdw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103056bWI5lr7yuRQZdB2D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103057quiSonXcPkF2hsOL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103100oTzGHgcXhU5mdpfK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/muji-carbonated-drinks\" rel=\"nofollow\">MUJI 在日本推出了第一款可乐饮料</a>，售价为 150 日元。不过，暂时只在日本地区发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102948sgyxVe8G403OD529.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>川久保玲为 COMME des GARÇONS 在纽约大都会艺术博物馆举办的展览带来了<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/met-cdg-comme-des-garcons-museum-poocket-shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">十多款限定单品</a>。包括 T 恤、钱夹、tote 包，当中最为瞩目的，要属以黑色麂皮打造，辅以金色 CdG logo 的 NikeLab x CDG Pegasus 83s 鞋款。该系列已于<a href=\"http://store.metmuseum.org\" rel=\"nofollow\">大都会艺术博物馆网店</a>发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103004getvKkWSHoJ6sEdO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103004v9k0ClAVxowugNpZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103005MQzSAtuJFLcl9BrT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103004lObwaJV8vZ9QShmL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705031030100NOp1WItqiAnMv7R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705031030319M8kVa4x17AXhKZf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103027reoyhaK5vlbgAw0s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103027wpbAYoaOVX8LPgQz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503103027NCJnFB0MvAs9D6mr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>以“中指猫”走红的美国滑板品牌 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/the-spring-17-collection-of-ripndip/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RIPNDIP</a>，这一季推出了多款 T 恤、滑板，以及帽子、袜子和拖鞋等小物，都很有趣。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102928iUSrvOquno2cCxfP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017050310292898O3caxqi5J4QmFs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705031029281mOw0EHfrlbcGsMP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705031029282kPoZqmx1UT9gDOt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102929g6LTaQhCcA2R37jl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102929JWgjiofy203QnGdU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102929jBSPphdNgqGYMkat.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705031029296B48GHKYrLVxpU0M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102939HhIQJSAfLnu0B4ex.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/05/02/nike-air-vapormax-day-to-night-collection/#slide-8\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike Air VaporMax 将于六月一日发布全新 Day To Night 系列</a>，男女款各三种全新配色，售价为 190 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705031028547XHR6rmkpgMAdNjG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102854n10bwpEcf5VKPWR7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102845KiLgBlNXkHeV5ZJb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102845F7vSDcTzYuMHJ5KV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102846RANd5pQyhvqbTf1J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102846iSfTHLKAv0slBk7z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102845uelSDjJhNwmcMsvA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170503102846FMXPzVwk2EntxQes.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/fragment-design-x-louis-vuitton-pop-up-london-harrods\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}